text: Masako Sakamoto (born 10 October 1972) is a Japanese badminton player. She competed in women's doubles at the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Japan Category:Badminton players at the 1996 Summer Olympics
